1. Did the Indian cricket team win the Cricket World Cup in 1983 and 2011 as claimed?
2. Were the Indian cricket team runners-up at the 2003 Cricket World Cup?
3. How many times has the Indian cricket team been knocked out in the group stage of the Cricket World Cup, and in which years did this occur?
